			<div class="content" id="post-content-4784718">
									

<p>It's an oversight on our part - there's no name change, the younger Bowe just has a different timeline than he's supposed to per Resurrection. (I've been omitting any mention of years in my tales so they don't contradict Res <em>or</em> gull). Since we have to ask permission to get on the hub anyway, just consider this an alternate timeline for the time being, one more in tune with gull's headcanon :P</p>
<p>If we try to get this series on the hub after the contest - and I'd very very much like to - we'll have an internal conversation about making those lines referring to the length of Bowe's absence match correctly. It's a very simple fix. Can't change anything before the contest's over, so for now just ignore those brief moments of temporal weirdness.</p>

