<p>The gun was meant to be a &quot;god killer.&quot; Within the tales, Bowe brought together The Children of the Scarlet King &amp; The Church of the Broken God. They each want to ressurect their Gods. Each group has a piece of what the other group needs to bring their god back. I believe Bowe was thinking that if they reached an agreement, and got their pieces back (The Seventh Son for TCSK and a missing part of the god for CoTBG) he would want to be able to kill the gods.</p>

